  ],
  "pages": [
    {
      "image": "assets/images/00.png",
      "en": "Drink Enough Water",
      "cn": "第 33 篇",
      "unit": 1
    },
    {
      "image": "assets/images/01.png",
      "en": "Water is really important for your body.",
      "cn": "水对你的身体非常重要。",
      "unit": 1
    },
    {
      "image": "assets/images/02.png",
      "en": "It helps keep you healthy and strong, making it easier for your brain to think and your body to move!",
      "cn": "它帮助你保持健康强壮，让你的大脑更容易思考，也让身体更容易活动！",
      "unit": 1
    },
    {
      "image": "assets/images/03.png",
      "en": "Sometimes, we forget to drink enough water.",
      "cn": "有时候，我们会忘记喝足够的水。",
      "unit": 1
    },
    {
      "image": "assets/images/04.png",
      "en": "Here are some fun ideas to help you drink more every day:",
      "cn": "这里有一些有趣的方法，帮助你每天多喝水：",
      "unit": 1
    },
    {
      "image": "assets/images/05.png",
      "en": "Get a Fun Water Bottle:",
      "cn": "准备一个有趣的水瓶：",
      "unit": 1
    },
    {
      "image": "assets/images/06.png",
      "en": "Get a water bottle in your favourite colour or with a cool design.",
      "cn": "准备一个你最喜欢颜色或有很酷设计的水瓶。",
      "unit": 2
    },
    {
      "image": "assets/images/07.png",
      "en": "This makes drinking water more fun!",
      "cn": "这会让喝水更有趣！",
      "unit": 2
    },
    {
      "image": "assets/images/08.png",
      "en": "Add Fruit to Your Water:",
      "cn": "给水里加水果：",
      "unit": 2
    },
    {
      "image": "assets/images/09.png",
      "en": "Try putting slices of orange, strawberries or lemon in your water.",
      "cn": "试着把橙子片、草莓或柠檬放进水里。",
      "unit": 2
    },
    {
      "image": "assets/images/10.png",
      "en": "It not only tastes great but also looks lovely!",
      "cn": "它不仅味道很棒，看起来也很漂亮！",
      "unit": 2
    },
    {
      "image": "assets/images/11.png",
      "en": "Set Reminders:",
      "cn": "设置提醒：",
      "unit": 3
    },
    {
      "image": "assets/images/12.png",
      "en": "Ask an adult to remind you to drink water during the day.",
      "cn": "请成年人提醒你白天喝水。",
      "unit": 3
    },
    {
      "image": "assets/images/13.png",
      "en": "You could also set a timer!",
      "cn": "你也可以设置一个计时器！",
      "unit": 3
    },
    {
      "image": "assets/images/14.png",
      "en": "Remember, drinking water helps you feel good, play well, and think clearly.",
      "cn": "记住，喝水能帮助你感觉良好、玩得开心、思考清楚。",
      "unit": 3
    },
    {
      "image": "assets/images/15.png",
      "en": "Let’s drink enough water every day so we can stay happy and healthy!",
      "cn": "让我们每天喝足够的水，这样就能保持快乐和健康！",
      "unit": 3
    }
  ],
